How can I generate a random playlist of 10 popular and upbeat songs using PHP? The songs must come from the genres of pop, hip-hop, and electronic dance music (EDM) and should be suitable for a lively celebration. Here is a possible PHP code:
$pop_songs = array("Shape of You", "Uptown Funk", "Happy", "I Gotta Feeling", "Can't Stop the Feeling!");
$hiphop_songs = array("HUMBLE.", "God's Plan", "In Da Club", "Lose Yourself", "All the Way Up");
$edm_songs = array("Levels", "Wake Me Up", "Silence", "Something Just Like This", "The Middle");
$playlist = array();
for($i = 0; $i < 10; $i++){
$genre = rand(1, 3);
switch($genre){
case 1:
$song = $pop_songs[rand(0, count($pop_songs) - 1)];
break;
case 2:
$song = $hiphop_songs[rand(0, count($hiphop_songs) - 1)];
break;
case 3:
$song = $edm_songs[rand(0, count($edm_songs) - 1)];
break;
}
array_push($playlist, $song);
}
echo "Here is your random playlist:
";
foreach($playlist as $index => $song){
echo ($index+1) . ". " . $song . "
";
}
